      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦王上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤王御驾到龙廷，文臣武将朝寡人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启奏万岁：小女昨晚得了疯病。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨晚灯光之下，还是好好的，怎么得了疯病？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天有不测风云，人有旦夕祸福。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤赐她龙车凤辇，带上金殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传御林军走上。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四卫卒同上。赵高领赵女同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "午门外下了那龙车凤辇，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "行一步来至在御驾跟前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "看昏王他把我怎样旨传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到于今顾不得抛头露面"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，上面就是万岁，上前参见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我晓得呀，上面敢是皇帝老官？恭喜你万福，贺喜你发财。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见了寡人，为何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你大人不下跪的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是个疯癫女子。寡人好笑，啊，哈哈哈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你好笑，我也好笑，哈哈哈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寡人笑你疯癫，你笑寡人何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你笑我疯癫，我就笑你无道的昏君。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寡人有道，怎说无道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，你要问你的无道，列位大人老哥听了。你也听了。只因老王在世，东修岱"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "海，西建阿房，南修乌陵，北造万里长城。实指望江山万代，谁想你这昏王贪"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "淫恋酒，不理朝事。我想这天下，乃人人之天下，并非你一人之天下，我看你"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这江山，未必能长久了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想此事气得我乌云扯乱，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "气得我舌尖儿咬破牙关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "殿前武士，刀门架起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了，我乃丞相之女，指挥老爷之妻，你们放肆大胆，还不与我退下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我手中有镔铁定要试斩，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将这班众狂徒立斩马前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再若提起疯癫，抓头来见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，再若提起疯癫，万岁就要杀头了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了，动不动你就要杀头，我且问你。一个人头，割将下来，难道还长得上么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长不上了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀啊啊啊，爹爹，我的儿啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我这里忙下金銮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那昏王怎知我袖内机关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵女",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵女下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老臣领罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罚俸三月，退班。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦王下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵高",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢主龙恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵高、四卫卒同下。）"
        }
      ],
